workflow.name: Target identification from GWAS summary statistics
workflow.description: Enables post-GWAS analyses for deeper interpretation of results, with the flexibility to activate specific analyses, such as fine-mapping, TWAS, variant-to-gene mapping, colocalization with GTEx eQTL data, and variant annotation of significant results with VEP.
